---
import BaseLayout from '../../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Divorce Lawyer Marketing Malaysia | SEO & Lead Generation for Family Law"
  description="Complete marketing guide for divorce lawyers in Malaysia. SEO strategies, Google Ads, content marketing, and lead generation for family law practices."
>
  <article class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 prose">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Marketing for Divorce Lawyers in Malaysia</h1>
      
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8">
        Divorce lawyers face unique marketing challenges. Your clients are going through one of life's most 
        difficult transitions. Here's how to reach them with empathy while building a sustainable practice.
      </p>

      <h2>Understanding Your Ideal Client</h2>
      <p>
        People searching for divorce lawyers are typically in emotional distress. They search differently than 
        someone looking for a corporate lawyer. Common search patterns include:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>"Divorce lawyer near me"</strong> – Location-based, ready to act</li>
        <li><strong>"How much does divorce cost Malaysia"</strong> – Early research stage</li>
        <li><strong>"Child custody lawyer KL"</strong> – Specific concern-driven</li>
        <li><strong>"Peguam perceraian"</strong> – Bahasa Malaysia searches</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>SEO Strategy for Divorce Lawyers</h2>
      <p>
        Local SEO is critical. Most clients want a lawyer nearby. Focus on:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Google Business Profile optimization</li>
        <li>Location-specific landing pages (e.g., "Divorce Lawyer Petaling Jaya")</li>
        <li>Content answering common divorce questions</li>
        <li>Reviews and testimonials (ethically compliant)</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Content Marketing Topics</h2>
      <p>
        Create helpful content that addresses real concerns:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Divorce process in Malaysia: Step-by-step guide</li>
        <li>Child custody laws: What you need to know</li>
        <li>Division of assets in Malaysian divorce</li>
        <li>Mutual vs contested divorce: What's the difference?</li>
        <li>How long does divorce take in Malaysia?</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Google Ads for Divorce Lawyers</h2>
      <p>
        Paid advertising can deliver immediate leads, but costs are high due to competition. 
        Focus on:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>High-intent keywords ("hire divorce lawyer KL")</li>
        <li>Negative keywords to filter out DIY seekers</li>
        <li>Landing pages optimized for conversion</li>
        <li>Call extensions for immediate contact</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Lead Generation Tactics</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Free consultation offer</strong> – Lowers barrier to contact</li>
        <li><strong>WhatsApp button</strong> – Preferred communication in Malaysia</li>
        <li><strong>FAQ chatbot</strong> – Answers common questions 24/7</li>
        <li><strong>Downloadable guides</strong> – "What to Prepare for Your First Meeting"</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Ethical Considerations</h2>
      <p>
        The Malaysian Bar Council has advertising rules. Ensure your marketing:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Doesn't make false promises about outcomes</li>
        <li>Maintains client confidentiality</li>
        <li>Doesn't disparage other lawyers</li>
        <li>Is dignified and professional</li>
      </ul>

      <div class="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-lg mt-8">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-2">Ready to Grow Your Family Law Practice?</h3>
        <p class="mb-4">We specialize in ethical, effective marketing for Malaysian law firms.</p>
        <a href="https://resultmarketing.asia" class="bg-primary text-white px-6 py-2 rounded-lg inline-block">
          Get a Free Consultation
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
